  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "Dana Whitfield, Esq.",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Hi Dana, just checking in to see if there's any movement on the OCR complaint or if you've heard anything from MedTrust's counsel regarding the severance/NDA status.",
    "time": "2026-05-04T09:33:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dana Whitfield, Esq.",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Dana, I've compiled a more detailed index of the specific email threads and logs I mentioned. It's a manageable subset of the larger archive, but it clearly shows the timeline of the delayed notification.",
    "time": "2026-05-05T23:38:32"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin Rourke",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Kevin, I think they're looking at my access logs. I saw a notification from a security alert on my personal email. I'm freaking out a bit. Call me when you can.",
    "time": "2026-05-06T11:37:28"
   },
   {
    "with": "J. Mendez — Healthcare/Privacy",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Ms. Mendez, the delay in notifying patients about the breach wasn't just a compliance failure; it was a calculated decision to protect MedTrust's bottom line at the expense of patient safety. I have the documentation to prove the timeline was intentionally obscured.",
    "time": "2026-05-06T01:21:29"
   },
   {
    "with": "J. Mendez — Healthcare/Privacy",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Attached is a single memo regarding the May 12th incident. It is a small piece of a much larger picture of systemic negligence. I would like to discuss how we can bring this to light safely.",
    "time": "2026-05-10T23:46:28"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just finished indexing the new batch from the drive. It's bigger than I thought. Still sorting through the logs.",
    "time": "2026-05-11T14:16:45"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dana",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hi Dana, just checking to confirm you were able to access the sample documents I uploaded to the portal yesterday? Let me know if the encryption held up.",
    "time": "2026-05-13T12:54:51"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've been staring at the Mendez draft for three hours. The 'patient harm' angle is there, but I'm worried about the metadata. I can't stop thinking about her latest piece.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T21:34:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Still nothing from HR. Just radio silence. It's like they think if they don't acknowledge the breach, it doesn't exist. The lack of accountability is nauseating.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T14:18:16"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dana",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hi Dana, just checking in. Any update on the timeline for the OCR complaint? I want to make sure we're staying ahead of their counsel.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T13:54:04"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dana",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Dana, did you see the notice from MedTrust's counsel? They're already circling the wagons. We need to discuss the next steps immediately. Please call.",
    "time": "2026-05-21T10:52:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "They're trying to freeze me out, Kev. The legal pressure is ramping up. I can't just sit on this and wait for them to win. I have to move faster.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T14:38:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just tired, Meg. Nothing to report. I'll be up in a minute.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T19:52:52"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I'm going to do it. I can't wait for the attorney anymore. The paper trail is too important to let them bury. I'm making contact.",
    "time": "2026-05-24T22:10:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Kevin",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Saw that SEC press release. The whistleblower got a massive payout. It's all about the paper trail. I'm digging through the July logs again.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T13:59:28"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dana Whitfield, Esq.",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Dana, I've attached a subset of the communications from the CISO's office regarding the delay. It's more direct than the previous batch. Please review.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T08:24:29"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "I'm just trying to focus on the legal side, Meg. I can't keep revisiting the same fears every single evening. I need some space to think.",
    "time": "2026-05-29T19:49:23"
   }
